WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:02.520
This is my nephew,

00:00:03.280 --> 00:00:04.576
Yuan Yuan.

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:06.096
He's five years old,

00:00:06.120 --> 00:00:07.400
super adorable.

00:00:08.360 --> 00:00:10.336
I asked him the other day,

00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:12.720
"What would you like
for your birthday this year?"

00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:17.440
He said, "I want to have
a one-way mirror Spider-Man mask."

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.776
I had absolutely no idea
what he was talking about,

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:22.776
so I said, "Wow, that's really cool,

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:24.372
but how are you going to get it?"

00:00:25.120 --> 00:00:28.016
He told me, without a blink of his eyes,

00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:32.119
"I'm going to tell my mom
and make a wish before I go to bed.